        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مِيرَاثُ اَللَّهِ مِنْ عَبْدِهِ اَلْمُؤْمِنِ اَلْوَلَدُ اَلصَّالِحُ يَسْتَغْفِرُ لَهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4689 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Allah's (swt) inheritance from His (swt) believing servant is a righteous child who seeks forgiveness for him.\""
